{"tid":1512580,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"越南電訊商：華為不安全 將與美國晶片公司合作","createTime":"2019-08-28T02:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T14:43:36.000Z","uid":144372,"like":237,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"3e41d853cdf467c9f4fe6e91f55f3e907c0c8dfb","tid":1512580,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:53:34.000Z","msg":"在美國拉攏封殺下，大陸電訊設備商華為再遇抵制。外電報導，越南有意成為首個提供5G網路的東協國家，並且不使用華為設備。分析認為，在華為問題上，越南正悄悄靠邊站在美國政府的一邊。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，越南國防部屬下、當地最大電訊商Viettel Group的CEO Le Dang Dung表示，越南將於河內部署愛立信（Ericsson）的設備，在胡志明市使用諾基亞（Nokia）的技術。它將使用高通和另一家美國公司的5G晶片組。而公司也正在開發自己的設備。<br />\n<br />\nLe Dang Dung受訪時稱，該公司目前無打算與華為合作，「現在對華為有點敏感。據說使用華為不安全」，公司立場是選擇更安全的設備，因而選擇歐洲的諾基亞和愛立信。他強調，Viettel不用華為是基於技術考慮，無關地緣政治因素。據了解，Viettel的4G網路也是使用該兩間公司的技術和設備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190827002319-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20190827002319-260408&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=22e281a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190827002319-260408</a>"},{"pid":"0495cf4b5a24f16fc33445b55f4818f24d0d359e","tid":1512580,"uid":284522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=3e91e218\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=5791b7b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=a0915a71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"42d5e907794188630f40178b4049d831ee0e8b34","tid":1512580,"uid":89145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:54:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e595cefc962a60e4a1eed40a9f6d1a17d6e32cce","tid":1512580,"uid":301523,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:54:15.000Z","msg":"想去越南玩好耐啦"},{"pid":"55f79f3462ae0f65d7a3736a95399ee1b51be61f","tid":1512580,"uid":197640,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"世界揀陣營落注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bddd6cd9ee2be9b1f2609a0ad25af79fd02cff4","tid":1512580,"uid":66719,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"55f79f3462ae0f65d7a3736a95399ee1b51be61f","tid":1512580,"uid":197640,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"世界揀陣營落注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:00:54.000Z","msg":"係時候要跟隊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d7cab059c8b3d79a0cbb09a6647e4cf15543a0","tid":1512580,"uid":40750,"like":8,"dislike":19,"score":-11,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:02:25.000Z","msg":"越共都唔撚撐共狗自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im